The '''Ministry of Health and Social Protection''' ({{lang-es|Ministerio de Salud y de Protección Social}}) is the [[ministries of Colombia|national executive ministry]] of the [[Government of Colombia]] responsible for coordinating and implementing the national policy and social services relating to [[Health care in Colombia|health]] and [[social security]].

